SB 2.0接口供电只有500mA，低于USB 3.0接口的900mA，则有可能出现供电不足，此时可以配上一个5V/1A~2A，外径：3.25mm，内径：1.3mm，内正外负的电源进行使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">*当计算机无USB 3.0接口时，可以通过在PC电脑主板上安装一个PCI-E USB 3.0转接卡，并对转接卡进行正确的驱动后方可使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb